Package clientGUI

Class ShopManagerGUIController

  • java.lang.Object
    • clientGUI.ShopManagerGUIController
  • public class ShopManagerGUIController
extends java.lang.Object
    ShopManagerGUIController class is responsible for the main GUI of each shop manager, it allows them to pick one of six desired actions that are made for shop managers to manage customers, workers and viewing reports.

    Project Name: Zer-Li (Flowers store in Java)

    Version:
    V1.00 2022
    Author:
    Habib Ibrahim, Vitaly Rofman, Ibrahim Daoud, Yosif Hosen
